{"tid":266714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"由NBA比賽時間來看 籃球員比足球員優勝","createTime":"2017-06-01T16:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T05:32:01.000Z","uid":118983,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cd6083e848ce5829ebecaf72aec45ffed5e34d","tid":266714,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"一般籃球員的比賽時間為本港時間的早上<br />\n足球比賽則為凌晨<br />\n<br />\n騎打勇的時間為早上 6月2日 9:00<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n德國杯決賽時間為 5月27日 深夜1:55<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由此可見 籃球員係番工時間打波 證明打籃球嘅薪金可以養起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n足球員比賽為夜晚 證明佢日頭仲要做奴工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籃球win <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04a5a209f9ddd1a44ea5955038a05fb065afef1","tid":266714,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee88d095b18c065b21ebafe0adf02e2b66f2916a","tid":266714,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d35208a889d33cdefba64acfb4a0c4acf98573","tid":266714,"uid":12634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"Sleep is for the weak<br />\n足球員凌晨踢完第二朝仲可以返工，啲體能真係唔係人咁品<br />\n<br />\n結論：足球完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fd8c7dc54bf595bce0b5dc00171002360d36ad","tid":266714,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a39acab5e2abdc4e1c1baa9f1549b1352de55765","tid":266714,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:32:29.000Z","m